    "notes": "Manual trigger only (active: false). Downloads historical odds from free external sources (aussportsbetting.com for NFL, sports-statistics.com for MLB), matches to existing game_results by (date, home_team, away_team), and upserts into fact_market_odds. Runs NFL and MLB sequentially. Requires openpyxl in the Sports container.",
